Durban &#8211; Photos of a Durban based lady in her early thirties &#8216;burning&#8217; from behind have since gone viral on picture sharing platform,Whatsapp and Facebook.The woman,identified as Lindiwe Dube,was promised to set herself alight and get a reward of R5000 by one bar owner based in Soweto,of which she later risked to the surprise of many. &#8221;I wonder why people love money like this,this is proof that people can do anything for money,this lady has no difference with Zodwa Wabantu&#8221;,said one of the ladies who declined to be named.&nbsp;!&nbsp;